<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 02:15:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>被称为“邪恶面孔”的哈马斯加沙首领位列以色列目标名单之首</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubbed-face-of-evil-hamas-gaza-chief-at-top-of-israels-target-list/articleshow/104481151.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481151.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔被认为是以色列军队计划入侵该飞地的首要目标。辛瓦尔在以色列监狱中服刑二十多年，于 2011 年获释。他被视为哈马斯内部的残暴执法者和以色列的死敌。据信他是最近造成 1,300 多名以色列人死亡的袭击事件的幕后黑手。辛瓦尔在汗尤尼斯长大，并于 1987 年帮助组建了哈马斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubbed-face-of-evil-hamas-gaza-chief-at-top-of-israels-target-list/articleshow/104481151.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列：哈马斯有199名人质，高于此前估计</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-has-199-hostages-higher-than-previously-estimated/articleshow/104481293.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481293.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方目前报告称，有 199 人被哈马斯劫持为人质，这一数字比以色列高级军官上周提供的至少 150 名人质的初步估计有所增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-has-199-hostages-higher-than-previously-estimated/articleshow/104481293.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京将于周三在中国会见习近平并举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-to-meet-xi-for-talks-in-china-on-wed/articleshow/104481496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京计划在北京举行的纪念中国“一带一路”倡议十周年论坛上会见中国领导人习近平。此外，普京在接受采访时强调，金砖国家在人口购买力平价方面已经超越了七国集团国家，并强调该集团作为西方主导的国际机构的替代方案的潜在好处。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-to-meet-xi-for-talks-in-china-on-wed/articleshow/104481496.cms</guid></item><item><title>强硬派共和党人竞选美国众议院议长获得支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hardline-republican-jim-jordan-picks-up-support-in-bid-for-us-house-speaker/articleshow/104481454.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481454.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;强硬派共和党人吉姆·乔丹的美国众议院议长竞选活动正在赢得支持。尽管遭到本党内部的反对，乔丹相信他有动力赢得周二的投票。共和党的内讧推迟了对联邦机构的资助以及对以色列和乌克兰的援助。约旦承诺优先考虑军事和支出立法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hardline-republican-jim-jordan-picks-up-support-in-bid-for-us-house-speaker/articleshow/104481454.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国寻求联合援助乌克兰和以色列</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-seeks-to-club-ukraine-and-israel-aid/articleshow/104481238.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481238.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府正在寻求国会批准一项紧急援助计划，其中包括对乌克兰的援助和对以色列的持续支持。这一战略承认这两场冲突的紧迫性，旨在通过将乌克兰与对以色列的援助联系起来，获得共和党对乌克兰的支持。此前，国会曾允许乌克兰的紧急资金失效。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-seeks-to-club-ukraine-and-israel-aid/articleshow/104481238.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称杀害了六名哈马斯高级官员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-killed-6-hamas-senior-men/articleshow/104481350.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481350.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;作为对 10 月 7 日开始的袭击的回应，以色列声称在报复性空袭中杀死了至少 6 名哈马斯高级领导人。然而，据巴勒斯坦卫生部称，这些空袭给加沙人民造成了严重伤亡，造成 2,750 人死亡、9,700 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:18:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-killed-6-hamas-senior-men/articleshow/104481350.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国誓言加强安全，因政府因“野蛮的伊斯兰恐怖主义”而受到批评</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-vows-to-boost-security-amid-criticism-of-govt-after-barbaric-islamic-terrorism/articleshow/104481075.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481075.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在最近发生一名教师被刺死事件后，法国计划加快驱逐激进外国人，并加强其移民法草案。政府面临右翼的批评，并部署了数千名士兵应对袭击。法国总统马克龙谴责这一事件是“野蛮的伊斯兰恐怖主义”。内政部长杰拉尔德·达尔马宁表示，政府将审查安全风险清单，并驱逐构成威胁的个人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-vows-to-boost-security-amid-criticism-of-govt-after-barbaric-islamic-terrorism/articleshow/104481075.cms</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚要求以色列特使因与哈马斯的战争发生争执而离开</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/colombia-demands-israel-envoy-leave-amid-spat-over-war-with-hamas/articleshow/104477515.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104477515.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哥伦比亚周一要求以色列大使离开这个南美国家，因为总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗关于与哈马斯战争的言论引发的争执不断恶化。周日，哥伦比亚军方主要武器供应国之一以色列表示，随着外交争端升级，它将“停止向这个南美国家进行安全出口”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 18:40:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/colombia-demands-israel-envoy-leave-amid-spat-over-war-with-hamas/articleshow/104477515.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔调解后俄罗斯归还四名乌克兰儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-returns-four-ukrainian-kids-after-qatari-mediation/articleshow/104480885.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104480885.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡塔尔政府宣布，四名与家人失散并被带到俄罗斯的乌克兰儿童已与家人团聚。卡塔尔在儿童回返谈判中发挥了调解人的作用，家庭团聚进程的成功标志着儿童与家人团聚迈出了重要一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:15:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-returns-four-ukrainian-kids-after-qatari-mediation/articleshow/104480885.cms</guid></item><item><title>世界绝不能像在朝鲜那样在伊朗问题上失败——联合国核负责人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-must-not-fail-in-iran-as-it-did-in-north-korea-un-nuclear-chief/articleshow/104478779.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104478779.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国核监督机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西警告说，国际社会决不能像在朝鲜那样在伊朗问题上失败。他对伊朗核计划表示担忧，并强调国际原子能机构（IAEA）在监测和防止核武器发展方面的重要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 22:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-must-not-fail-in-iran-as-it-did-in-north-korea-un-nuclear-chief/articleshow/104478779.cms</guid></item><item><title>布鲁塞尔枪击案两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/two-killed-in-brussels-shooting/articleshow/104478299.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104478299.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;比利时首都检察官办公室称，周一晚间布鲁塞尔发生枪击事件，造成两人死亡，嫌疑人正在逃亡。检察官发言人表示，调查已经展开，但没有推测枪手的动机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 21:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/two-killed-in-brussels-shooting/articleshow/104478299.cms</guid></item><item><title>将军表示，俄罗斯的目标是突破乌克兰东北部的防御</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-aims-to-pierce-ukraine-defences-in-northeast-general-says/articleshow/104480645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104480645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰地面部队指挥官表示，俄罗斯的目标是突破库皮安斯克-莱曼地区的乌克兰防御。该地区的战斗急剧增加​​，据称俄罗斯派遣人员并准备进攻行动。库皮安斯克和莱曼镇是乌克兰将俄罗斯军队驱逐出顿巴斯工业中心地带的关键镇。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 23:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-aims-to-pierce-ukraine-defences-in-northeast-general-says/articleshow/104480645.cms</guid></item><item><title>5 名以色列人对在塞浦路斯酒店房间强奸一名英国妇女的指控表示无罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/5-israelis-plead-not-guilty-to-charges-of-raping-a-british-woman-in-a-cyprus-hotel-room/articleshow/104478408.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104478408.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五名被控在塞浦路斯酒店房间轮奸一名英国妇女的以色列人对所有指控均表示无罪。审判定于12月18日恢复，届时警方调查人员将为检方作证。这名 20 岁的女子认出了五名以色列人，并声称他们强行将她带到一个房间，在那里对她进行了强奸和性侵犯。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 21:54:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/5-israelis-plead-not-guilty-to-charges-of-raping-a-british-woman-in-a-cyprus-hotel-room/articleshow/104478408.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯和内塔尼亚胡在特拉维夫的空袭警报中躲进地堡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blinken-netanyahu-shelter-in-bunker-amid-air-raid-sirens-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/104477347.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104477347.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务院发言人马修·米勒表示，周一，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯和以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在特拉维夫会面时，空袭警报响起，他们在掩体中避难了五分钟。他说，所有与会者都已离开掩体，继续开会，并前往以色列国防部指挥中心继续讨论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 18:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blinken-netanyahu-shelter-in-bunker-amid-air-raid-sirens-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/104477347.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔厨师荣获新加坡《厨艺大师》第四季冠军</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-chef-crowned-winner-of-masterchef-singapore-season-4/articleshow/104480981.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104480981.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度裔新加坡人 Inderpal Singh 赢得了《新加坡厨艺大师》第四季的冠军。辛格是一位家庭餐饮企业主，带走了 10,000 新元现金和其他礼物。他以76.6分（满分90分）的成绩获得三人赛冠军，领先亚军3.6分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-chef-crowned-winner-of-masterchef-singapore-season-4/articleshow/104480981.cms</guid></item><item><title>“参加一个又一个葬礼”：男子回忆哈马斯袭击以色列音乐节的恐怖故事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/going-to-funeral-after-funeral-man-recalls-horror-tale-of-hamas-attack-on-israel-music-festival/articleshow/104476992.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104476992.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列音乐节上哈马斯袭击的幸存者盖尔·卡茨 (Gal Katz) 在橘子林中躲藏了六个小时，直到以色列士兵赶到才成功逃脱。卡茨描述了这场导致 250 多人丧生的大屠杀，以及他的朋友们如何无法逃脱。作为报复，以色列对加沙发动袭击，造成至少2670人死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 18:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/going-to-funeral-after-funeral-man-recalls-horror-tale-of-hamas-attack-on-israel-music-festival/articleshow/104476992.cms</guid></item><item><title>要求向被围困的加沙提供援助的呼声越来越高</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/calls-mount-to-let-aid-in-to-besieged-gaza/articleshow/104476566.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104476566.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;援助机构周一呼吁允许重要的人道主义物资进入加沙地带，并警告说，随着供水枯竭、食品和燃料库存减少，拯救数百万人的时间已经不多了。但这样做——并切断水、食品和燃料供应直至冲突结束——给已经在长达数年的封锁下苦苦挣扎的领土带来了额外的压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 17:18:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/calls-mount-to-let-aid-in-to-besieged-gaza/articleshow/104476566.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登可能的以色列之行充满安全和政治挑战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/potential-biden-trip-to-israel-rife-with-security-political-challenges/articleshow/104476131.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104476131.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府正在考虑可能访问以色列，以应对安全和政治挑战。虽然这次访问可以被视为对总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的支持，但也可能使拜登总统有影响该地区事件的影响力。拜登表达了对以色列和巴勒斯坦的支持，与内塔尼亚胡的会面可能会允许私下讨论有关地面入侵加沙的担忧和潜在的红线。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 16:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/potential-biden-trip-to-israel-rife-with-security-political-challenges/articleshow/104476131.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国增加对巴勒斯坦人的援助1000万英镑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/britain-increases-aid-to-palestinians-by-10-million-pounds/articleshow/104475497.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104475497.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相苏纳克周一表示，英国将增加对巴勒斯坦人民的援助 1000 万英镑（1218 万美元），以应对加沙的人道主义危机，同时他呼吁以色列尽力减少平民伤亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 15:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/britain-increases-aid-to-palestinians-by-10-million-pounds/articleshow/104475497.cms</guid></item><item><title>太重而无法飞行：为相扑选手预订特别航班</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-airlines-arranges-extra-flight-for-sumo-wrestlers-due-to-weight-restrictions-on-plane/articleshow/104475146.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104475146.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本航空不得不安排额外的航班来容纳参加体育节的相扑选手。摔跤手的体重引起了人们对燃油容量的担忧，因为他们的平均体重为 120 公斤，而乘客通常的平均体重为 70 公斤。由于原航班的重量限制，航空公司不得不将摔跤手转移到专门安排的航班上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 15:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-airlines-arranges-extra-flight-for-sumo-wrestlers-due-to-weight-restrictions-on-plane/articleshow/104475146.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>